# Design System Standards

Always use these CSS custom properties - never hardcode values:

## Colors
- Primary: --primary (#2563eb), --primary-dark (#1e40af), --primary-light (#3b82f6)
- Secondary: --secondary (#10b981), --accent (#8b5cf6)
- Text: --text-dark (#1f2937), --text-body (#4b5563), --text-light (#6b7280)
- Backgrounds: --bg-white (#ffffff), --bg-light (#f9fafb), --bg-gray (#f3f4f6)
- Gradients: --gradient-primary (135deg, #667eea 0%, #764ba2 100%)

## Typography
- Font: --font-primary (-apple-system, BlinkMacSystemFont, 'Segoe UI', Roboto, sans-serif)
- Display font: --font-display ('Inter', sans-serif) from Google Fonts
- Sizes: --text-xs through --text-5xl (0.75rem to 3rem)
- Weights: --font-normal (400) through --font-extrabold (800)
- Line heights: --leading-tight (1.25), --leading-normal (1.6), --leading-relaxed (1.8)

## Spacing
- Use spacing scale: --space-1 through --space-24 (0.25rem to 6rem)
- Never use arbitrary values like padding: 23px

## Components
- Border radius: Small (10px), Medium (15px), Large (20px), Full (50px)
- Shadows: Light (0 5px 20px rgba(0,0,0,0.08)), Medium (0 10px 30px rgba(0,0,0,0.15))
- Transitions: Standard (all 0.3s ease)

## Animation Guidelines
- Use transform and opacity only for performance
- Standard duration: 0.3s for hovers, 0.8s for entrances
- Always respect prefers-reduced-motion
